PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION whereby the TSARTLIP BAND surrenders, for a term of 25 years and six months, any of its rights and interest in some 0.284 hectares of land on South Saanich Indian Reserve No. 1 in BRITISH COLUMBIA, for the purpose of leasing them to the Native Participation Committee for an Aboriginal Sport Development Centre.
